---
title: Thai Prawn Rice with Lime and Coriander
description: Looking for a tasty midweek dinner option? Try cooking up our Prawn Rice with Lime and Coriander in just 20 minutes for a balanced and tasty dinnertime.
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/thai-prawn-rice-dfb5d002-3b3042d2.jpg
